ghost-role-information-fish-ghost-character-spawner-name = Ghost Character Spawner (1 Slot)
ghost-role-information-fish-ghost-character-spawner-description = Join as your own character from Character Setup. You spawn naked at this location with no equipment. Only one player can take this role.

ghost-role-information-fish-ghost-character-spawner-syndicate-name = Ghost Character Spawner (1 Slot, Syndicate)
ghost-role-information-fish-ghost-character-spawner-syndicate-description = Join as your own character from Character Setup. You spawn naked with Syndicate and Pirate factions, can use Syndicate biocode items, and are ignored by Syndicate and Pirate turrets. Only one player can take this role.

ghost-role-information-fish-ghost-character-spawner-pirate-name = Ghost Character Spawner (1 Slot, Pirate)
ghost-role-information-fish-ghost-character-spawner-pirate-description = Join as your own character from Character Setup. You spawn naked with the Pirate faction and are ignored by Pirate turrets. Only one player can take this role.
